#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:1
msgid "Security, backup and safety when using the Dash Electrum wallet"
msgstr "使用达世币轻钱包时的安全和备份事宜"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:1
msgid "dash, wallet, electrum, safety, password, backup, security, restore"
msgstr "达世币，钱包，轻钱包，安全，密码，备份，安全，恢复"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:8
msgid "Wallet security"
msgstr "钱包的安全"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:11
msgid "Change password"
msgstr "更改密码"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:13
msgid ""
"To change the wallet's password, select the **Wallet > Password** option "
"from the main menu, or click on the lock icon in the lower right of the main"
" window. Enter and confirm a new secure password. Should you forget your "
"wallets' password, all is not lost. Your wallet can be restored in its "
"entirety using the backup procedure described here."
msgstr ""
"如需修改密码，用户需要从主菜单中选择 **钱包 > 密码** "
"，或单击主窗口右下角的锁定图标。随后，用户需要输入并确认新的安全密码。需要牢记的是，如果用户忘记密码，那么相关数据和资金并不会丢失，用户还能通过本文档中介绍的备份程序的恢复步骤来复原钱包。"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:22
msgid "Backup"
msgstr "备份"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:24
msgid ""
"In Dash Electrum, a seed is a complete backup of all addresses and "
"transactions. Access your wallet's seed through the seed icon in the lower "
"right of the main screen, or the **Wallet > Seed** main menu option. When "
"prompted, enter the secure password you chose when setting up the Dash "
"Electrum wallet."
msgstr ""
"在达世币轻钱包中，种子指的是所有地址和交易数据的完整备份。用户可以通过主屏右下方的种子图标或主菜单选项 **钱包 > 种子** "
"来获取种子。一旦界面弹出提示，用户可在安装达世币轻钱包的时候设置安全密码。"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:33
msgid "Displaying the wallet recovery seed in Dash Electrum"
msgstr "在达世币轻钱包中显示的钱包恢复种子"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:35
msgid ""
"Hand-copy the twelve words found in the box to a piece of paper and store it"
" in a safe location. Remember, anyone who finds your seed can spend all of "
"the funds in your wallet."
msgstr "将密码框中的十二个字符密码记录到纸上并妥善保管。请牢记，任何拥有这个种子的个人都可以花费相应钱包中的所有资金。"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:42
msgid "Viewing the recovery seed"
msgstr "查看恢复种子"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:44
msgid ""
"Alternatively, a backup file can be saved using the **File > Save Copy** "
"main menu option. This file stores the wallet's encrypted seed along with "
"any imported addresses. Restoring this backup will require the wallet "
"password."
msgstr ""
"此外，用户还可以通过主菜单选项 **文件 > 保存副本** "
"来进行存储。这个备份文件包含钱包的加密种子和所有的导入地址。如需恢复备份，用户则需要用到钱包密码。"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:51
msgid "Restore"
msgstr "恢复"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:53
msgid ""
"The only thing needed to recover a Dash Electrum wallet on another computer "
"is its seed. You can test wallet recovery with your current installation of "
"Dash Electrum by removing the wallet data from the application data folder. "
"This optional procedure is described below. Before continuing, verify that "
"your seed is written down clearly and correctly on paper."
msgstr ""
"如需在另一台计算机上恢复达世币轻钱包，用户唯一需要用到的就是种子。用户可以从应用程序数据文件夹中删除钱包数据，以此测试当前安装的达世币轻钱包的恢复情况，具体步骤如下所示。在进行后续操作之前，请用户务必确认种子已经清晰无误地记录下来了。"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:60
msgid ""
"To get Dash Electrum to generate a new wallet, the old wallet data needs to "
"be deleted. Begin by closing Dash Electrum. Next, locate the application "
"data folder according to your operating system:"
msgstr "如需生成达世币轻钱包的新钱包，用户需要删除旧的钱包数据。用户首先需要关闭达世币轻钱包，然后再根据个人的操作系统找到应用程序的数据文件夹："

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:64
msgid "**Linux:**"
msgstr "**Linux:**"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:66
msgid ""
"Open Files, select **Go > Go to folder**, copy the path ``~/.electrum`` and "
"paste it into the dialog box"
msgstr "打开文件夹，选择 **访问 > 访问文件夹** ，然后将路径 ``~/.electrum``  复制粘贴到对话框中"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:68
#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:74
#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:80
msgid "Delete all files in the folder"
msgstr "删除文件夹中的所有文件"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:70
msgid "**macOS:**"
msgstr "**macOS:**"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:72
msgid ""
"Open Finder, select **Go > Go to Folder**, copy the path ``~/.electrum`` and"
" paste it into the dialog box"
msgstr "打开文件夹，选择 **访问 > 访问文件夹** ，然后将路径 ``~/.electrum`` 复制粘贴到对话框中"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:76
msgid "**Windows:**"
msgstr "**Windows:**"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:78
msgid ""
"Open Explorer, copy the path ``%APPDATA%\\Electrum-DASH`` and paste it in to"
" the address bar"
msgstr "打开Explorer浏览器，然后将路径 ``%APPDATA%\\Electrum-DASH`` 复制粘贴到地址栏中"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:82
msgid ""
"Having cleared the data directory, restart Dash Electrum. A dialog will "
"appear asking you to name your new wallet. Enter a name, select **Standard "
"wallet** as the wallet type and then choose **I already have a seed**."
msgstr ""
"清除数据目录后，用户需要重新启动达世币轻钱包。此时，界面将会出现一个对话框，要求用户为新钱包命名。根据提示，用户可输入名称，选择 **标准钱包** "
"作为钱包类型，然后再选择 **已有种子** 。"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:90
msgid "Restoring a wallet from an existing seed"
msgstr "借助现有的种子备份钱包"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:92
msgid "Next, copy the twelve word seed into the text field."
msgstr "接下来，用户需要将十二个字符的种子复制粘贴到文本框中。"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:97
msgid "Entering the recovery seed"
msgstr "输入恢复种子"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:99
msgid ""
"If your seed was entered correctly, Dash Electrum gives you the option to "
"add a password for your wallet. After restoring your wallet, Dash Electrum "
"will list any existing transactions from this wallet. This process may take "
"a few minutes, and the transactions may appear as **Not Verified**. This "
"problem disappears after restarting the program."
msgstr ""
"如果用户输入了正确的种子，那么达世币轻钱包就会提示用户为钱包添加密码。在钱包恢复后，达世币轻钱包将列出这个钱包中所有的现有交易。这个过程可能需要花费几分钟的时间，而交易可能会显示为"
" **未经验证** 。在程序重新启动后，这个问题就会自行解决。"

#: ../../wallets/electrum/security.rst:108
msgid "Unverified transactions after recovery"
msgstr "恢复钱包后显示的未经验证交易"
